Assign permissions to let users administer and view the Customer Insights app.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition. Requires a CRM Analytics Growth or CRM Analytics Plus license.

Permission Sets Needed:
Manage CRM Analytics Templated Apps
Use CRM Analytics Templated Apps

Assign Permissions to Admins
From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Users, and then select Users.
Click the name of the user.
Click Permission Set Assignments, and then click Edit Assignments.
Select the CRM Analytics Plus Admin permission set.
Click Add, and save your changes.

Assign Permissions to Users
From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Users, and then select Users.
Click the name of the user.
Click Permission Set Assignments, and then click Edit Assignments.
Select the CRM Analytics Plus User permission set.
Click Add, and save your changes.
title: Assigning Permissions to Customer Insights App in Salesforce
